'''2014年奧克尼地震'''在2014年8月5日12時22分33秒（[[南非標準時間|南非標準時間]]）發生，[[震央|震央]]位於[[南非|南非]][[西北省_(南非)|西北省]][[克萊克斯多普|克萊克斯多普]]的[[金礦開採|金礦]]城鎮[[奧克尼_(西北省)|奧克尼]]附近。南非地質科學委員會把此次地震的震級定為[[黎克特制|黎克特制]]5.5級<ref name=CGS/><ref name=Raaff>{{cite news |last1=Raaff |first1=Miranda |title=Quake measured 5.5: SA council |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/quake-measured-5-5-sa-council-1.1730900#.U-I-saiSySo |newspaper=IOL |accessdate=2014-08-06 |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCD949x?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/quake-measured-5-5-sa-council-1.1730900#.U-I-saiSySo |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Intensity |url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1625:intensity&catid=141:seismology&Itemid=615 |publisher=CGS |accessdate=2014-08-14 |quote=The Seismology Unit of the Council for Geoscience uses the Richter Scale, also known as the local magnitude scale, to determine the size of earthquakes. |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rq9bJqaG?url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，使之成為{{en-link|南非地震列表|List of earthquakes in South Africa|1969年圖爾巴地震}}（震級為黎克特制6.3級<ref>{{cite news |last1=Gifford |first1=Gill |title=Disaster teams out in full after SA quake |url=http://www.enca.com/disaster-teams-out-full-after-sa-quake |newspaper=eNCA |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqE3tIvQ?url=http://www.enca.com/disaster-teams-out-full-after-sa-quake |archivedate=2014-08-15 |date=2014-08-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>）以來，南非最嚴重的地震<ref name=Crowley/>。[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]估計，此次地震的[[震源深度|震源深度]]達{{convert|4.1|km|mi}}<ref name=USGS/>。該局表示，此次地震「極為危險」，因為震央位於克萊克斯多普和奧克尼附近<ref>{{cite news |title=SA quake severely dangerous – US Geological Survey |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/SA-quake-severely-dangerous-US-Geological-Survey-20140805 |newspaper=News24 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCUTnF7?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/SA-quake-severely-dangerous-US-Geological-Survey-20140805 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。地球科學委員會在8月5日錄得84次[[地震序列|餘震]]，並在8月6日錄得31次餘震，這些餘震的震級由黎克特制1.0級至3.8級不等<ref name=CGSaftershocks/>。地球科學委員會表示，此次地震是南非史上最嚴重的採礦誘發地震<ref name=Bateman>{{cite web |last1=Bateman |first1=Barry |title=SA EARTHQUAKE WAS MINE-RELATED |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/18/Earthquake-was-mine-related |website=Eyewitness News |accessdate=2014-08-18 |date=2014-08-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RvEQcXlY?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/18/Earthquake-was-mine-related |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 起因 ==
[[File:Seismicity_map_South_Africa.jpg|thumb]]繪製的南非地震活動圖]]
=== 地震活動史 ===
一般而言，地震在南非並不常見<ref>{{cite news |title=More tremors rock Stilfontein after quake |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/more-tremors-rock-stilfontein-after-quake-1.235903#.U_HNhsWSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-18 |work=IOL |agency=SAPA |date=2005-03-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rutk5AOs?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/more-tremors-rock-stilfontein-after-quake-1.235903#.U_HNhsWSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。這次地震在一個採礦地帶發生，而在這個地帶，地震是較為常見的<ref name=Hosken/>。地震發生前四年內，西北省一共錄得6次地震<ref name=Hosken/>。2005年，與奧克尼位處同一個地區的{{en-link|史蒂爾方丹|Stilfontein}}發生了一場震級達到黎克特制5.3級的地震，而地球科學委員會則一度形容這場地震是「南非最嚴重的採礦誘發地震」<ref>{{cite web |title=The Stilfontein Earthquake |url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1618:the-stilfontein-earthquake&Itemid=101 |publisher=CGS |accessdate=2014-08-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rq9FzIK3?url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。這次地震在2005年3月9日發生，震央位於史蒂爾方丹的哈特比斯方丹礦場（Hartebeesfontein mine；由{{en-link|DRDGOLD公司|DRDGOLD Limited}}經營）<ref>{{cite news |last1=Templeton |first1=Alameen |last2=Tau |first2=Poloko |last3=Ancer |first3=Jonathan |title=DRDGold 'doing the dirty' to Stilfontein |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/drdgold-doing-the-dirty-to-stilfontein-1.237033#.U_HVvcWSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-18 |work=IOL |date=2005-03-23 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RuvrbPJu?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/drdgold-doing-the-dirty-to-stilfontein-1.237033#.U_HVvcWSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，引致2人死亡，事後礦場亦須關閉<ref name=Raaff/><ref name=Hosken/><ref name=leCordeur/><ref>{{cite web |title=Media Update: 5.5 magnitude earthquake – tremors continue |url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2090:media-release-5-5-magnitude-earthquake-tremors-continue&catid=288:latest-news&Itemid=226 |publisher=CGS |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rq9MtQhW?url=http://www.geoscience.org.za/index.php?option=com_content |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。地震發生後，礦業監管部門進行調查，發現這次地震由採礦活動引發，並指出採礦活動可能會引發更多地震。調查報告書列出改善地震監測系統等多項建議<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mawson |first1=Nicola |title=Expert team to tackle SA mining's seismic challenges |url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/expert-team-to-tackle-sa-minings-seismic-challenges-2005-10-19 |accessdate=2014-08-18 |work=Mining Weekly |date=2005-10-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RuvAY99y?url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/expert-team-to-tackle-sa-minings-seismic-challenges-2005-10-19 |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Webb |first1=Mariaan |title=Study calls for improved seismic monitoring |url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/study-calls-for-improved-seismic-monitoring-2006-08-21 |accessdate=2014-08-18 |work=Mining Weekly |date=2006-08-21 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RuuT0iuW?url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/study-calls-for-improved-seismic-monitoring-2006-08-21 |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而報告書列出的部分建議已經在2014年發生地震之前付諸實行<ref name=Kolver/>。2014年6月15日，美國地質調查局在同一個地區錄得一場[[矩震級|矩震級]]達4.9M<sub>W</sub>的地震；[[地球科學|地球科學]]顧問克里斯·哈特納迪博士（Dr Chris Hartnady）認為，這次地震可能是一次[[前震|前震]]<ref name=Hosken/><ref name=leCordeur/>。

=== 專家意見 ===
[[比勒陀利亞大學|比勒陀利亞大學]]自然災害中心教授安德烈·基伊科（Andrzej Kijko）表示，採礦活動可以令天然斷層變得活躍。他相信，南非超過90%的地震都是由採礦活動（特別是在克萊克斯多普、[[卡雷頓維爾|卡雷頓維爾]]和[[韋爾科姆|韋爾科姆]]一帶進行的採礦活動）引發<ref name=Hosken/><ref name=Brace/><ref name=Kolver>{{cite news |last1=Kolver |first1=Leandi |title=More than 90% of SA seismic events are mining related – professor |url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/more-than-90-of-sa-seismic-events-are-mining-related-professor-2014-08-18 |accessdate=2014-08-19 |work=Mining Weekly |date=2014-08-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RwJ8TwF9?url=http://www.miningweekly.com/article/more-than-90-of-sa-seismic-events-are-mining-related-professor-2014-08-18 |archivedate=2014-08-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。哈特納迪則表示：「非洲這一部分靠近[[東非裂谷|東非裂谷]]體系，這個裂谷每年會擴闊數毫米。」他又說「地震的成因是斷層線滑動，積累的彈性能釋放出來」，而採礦活動可能引發了這場地震<ref name=Hosken/><ref name=Seale>{{cite news |last1=Seale |first1=Lebogang |title=Quake triggered by mine activity – expert |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/free-state/quake-triggered-by-mine-activity-expert-1.1731225#.U-zSfOOSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=The Star |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rp9VfULq?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/free-state/quake-triggered-by-mine-activity-expert-1.1731225#.U-zSfOOSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。基伊科和哈特納迪都相信，和1969年圖爾巴地震不同的是，這次地震是採礦誘發地震，這種地震在南非比自然地震常見<ref name=Brace/><ref name=Seale/><ref name=leCordeur>{{cite news |last1=le Cordeur |first1=Matthew |title=Did mining cause SA quake? |url=http://www.fin24.com/Companies/Mining/Did-mining-cause-Jhb-quake-20140806 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=Fin24 |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RpRgd4v0?url=http://www.fin24.com/Companies/Mining/Did-mining-cause-Jhb-quake-20140806 |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[金山大學|金山大學]][[地球物理學家|地球物理學家]]穆薩·曼齊（Musa Manzi）表示，這次地震可能是由採礦活動引發<ref name=Crowley>{{cite news |last1=Crowley |first1=Kevin |title=AngloGold Rejects Blame for Quake Even as Scientists Await Proof |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-08-11/anglogold-swings-to-loss-on-ghana-mali-mine-closing-costs.html |accessdate=2014-08-17 |newspaper=Bloomberg |date=2014-08-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RtUMmoDO?url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-08-11/anglogold-swings-to-loss-on-ghana-mali-mine-closing-costs.html |archivedate=2014-08-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而同一所大學的地震學家雷·杜爾海姆教授（Ray Durrheim）則表示，只要採礦活動在當地進行，地震活動就會持續下去<ref name=Bateman/>，甚至會持續到採礦活動結束後的一段很長的時間。他說廢棄礦山的積水也會對地質斷層施加壓力，並引發更多地震<ref name=Kolver/>。杜爾海姆還指出，採礦與地震「有持續的聯繫，一開始地震純粹是由採礦活動引發，後來（採礦活動停止後）自然地震也會因此發生。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Wakefield |first1=Adam |title=Quake possibly linked to mining – prof |url=http://www.iol.co.za/business/news/quake-possibly-linked-to-mining-prof-1.1737116#.U_MAysWSyyg |newspaper=Business Report |accessdate=2014-08-19 |date=2014-08-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RwHdMCbX?url=http://www.iol.co.za/business/news/quake-possibly-linked-to-mining-prof-1.1737116#.U_MAysWSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>」[[約翰內斯堡大學|約翰內斯堡大學]][[構造地質學|構造地質學]]專家赫爾曼·范涅克爾克博士（Dr Herman van Niekerk）相信，地震是[[非洲|非洲]]大陸慢慢分開的結果。美國地質調查局初時估計的震源深度是{{convert|10|km|mi|abbr=on}}，而礦井的最大深度則在{{convert|4|km|mi}}以內。范涅克爾克比較了兩組數據，並推斷這次地震不太可能由採礦活動引發<ref name=MG/><ref>{{cite news |title=USGS: Earthquake hits SA |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/05/USGS-Earthquake-hits-SA |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=EWN |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RpKREn6B?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/05/USGS-Earthquake-hits-SA |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/African-continent-split-likely-cause-of-quake-expert-20140806 |title=African continent split likely cause of quake – expert |newspaper=News24 |date=2014-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDNU6rk?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/African-continent-split-likely-cause-of-quake-expert-20140806 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Tempelhoff |first1=Elise |last2=Cilliers |first2=Susan |url=http://www.beeld.com/nuus/2014-08-06-s-skeur-afrika-stadig-in-twee |title=Só skeur Afrika (stadig) in twee |newspaper=Beeld |language=af |date=2014-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqcE6AgZ?url=http://www.beeld.com/nuus/2014-08-06-s-skeur-afrika-stadig-in-twee |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 地球科學委員會 ===
地球科學委員會的米歇爾·格羅貝拉（Michelle Grobbelaar）說：「根據經驗法則，如果你以前經歷過一次有相當強度的地震，你總會預料到當地會發生強度相若的地震。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kubheka |first1=Thando |last2=Kalenga |first2=Aurelie |title=Earthquake: Aftershocks Imminent |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/Earthquake-Aftershocks-imminent |accessdate=2014-08-15 |work=EWN |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqUZlNH6?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/Earthquake-Aftershocks-imminent |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>」格羅貝拉和來自同一個組織的丹佛·貝奇（Denver Birch）表示，由於地震在礦區發生，而在歷史上，當地又沒有地震數據，因此地震的成因難以確定<ref>{{cite news |title=UPDATE: Cause of the earthquake difficult to determine |url=http://sandtonchronicle.co.za/99196/earth-tremor-shakes-jozi/ |accessdate=2014-08-15 |newspaper=Sandton Chronicle |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqdwyoOv?url=http://sandtonchronicle.co.za/99196/earth-tremor-shakes-jozi/ |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Mosamo |first1=Sebabatso |title=Cause of SA Earthquake Uncertain |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/SA-earthquake-cause-uncertain |accessdate=2014-08-15 |newspaper=EWN |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqeCzshw?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/SA-earthquake-cause-uncertain |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。該會員工伊恩·桑德斯（Ian Saunders）確認，該會會把調查隊派往災區，進行深入調查<ref name=Hosken/>，而來自同一個組織的埃爾德里奇·卡斯瓦內（Eldridge Kgaswane）則說，他們應該能夠在一個月內確定地震的成因。卡斯瓦內表示：「事實上，（當地）最深的礦井比震源更淺，不過這並不表示採礦不可能是地震的成因。在大斷層附近進行爆破作業有可能引發（這次）地震活動。<ref name=Crowley/>」 2014年8月18日，地球科學委員會在[[比勒陀利亞|比勒陀利亞]]一場由{{en-link|科學和工業研究委員會|Council for Scientific and Industrial Research}}舉辦的講座上證實本次地震由與採礦有關的活動引發，令這次地震成為南非史上最嚴重的採礦誘發地震<ref name=Bateman/>。

== 影響 ==
=== 影響範圍 ===
感受到這次地震的範圍最遠可達到與奧克尼相距{{convert|600|km|mi}}的地區<ref name=MN>{{cite news |title=Quake kills one and injures multiple mineworkers |url=http://www.miningne.ws/2014/08/06/quake-kills-one-and-injures-multiple-mineworkers/ |accessdate=2014-08-16 |work=Mining News |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816082644/http://www.miningne.ws/2014/08/06/quake-kills-one-and-injures-multiple-mineworkers/ |archivedate=2014-08-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name=Hosken>{{cite news |last1=Hosken |first1=Graeme |last2=Smillie |first2=Shaun |last3=Child |first3=Katharine |last4=Louw |first4=Poppy |last5=Masombuka |first5=Sipho |url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/thetimes/2014/08/06/quake-of-shaky-things-to-come |title=Quake of shaky things to come |newspaper=Times LIVE |date=2014-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqElZkzA?url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/thetimes/2014/08/06/quake-of-shaky-things-to-come |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。南非的鄰國[[博茨瓦納|博茨瓦納]]、[[史瓦濟蘭|史瓦濟蘭]]、[[萊索托|萊索托]]和[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]]都能感到震動<ref name=Brace/><ref>{{cite news |title=Miners treated for injuries following quake |url=http://www.sabc.co.za/news/a/49ce298044fe0f21891899a5ad025b24/Miners-treated-for-injuries-following-quake-20140805 |date=2014-08-05 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=SABC News |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCjQZ1w?url=http://www.sabc.co.za/news/a/49ce298044fe0f21891899a5ad025b24/Miners-treated-for-injuries-following-quake-20140805 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=BBC1>{{cite news |title=Earthquake shakes South Africa killing one |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-28663595 |newspaper=BBC News |accessdate=2014-08-06 |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqE99gLO?url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-28663595 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。當時人們要從[[布隆方丹|布隆方丹]]最高的兩座大樓（前{{en-link|查爾斯·羅伯茨·斯瓦特|Charles Robberts Swart|C·R·斯瓦特}}大廈和萊博杭大廈）<ref>{{cite news |title=Quake empties Bloem's tall buildings |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/free-state/quake-empties-bloem-s-tall-buildings-1.1730950#.U-Ofe6iSySo |newspaper=IOL |agency=SAPA |accessdate=2014-08-07 |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCoYXTW?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/free-state/quake-empties-bloem-s-tall-buildings-1.1730950#.U-Ofe6iSySo |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[比勒陀利亞|比勒陀利亞]]的高樓大廈、[[比勒陀利亞大學|比勒陀利亞大學]]教學大樓和[[德班|德班]]{{en-link|南非稅務局|South African Revenue Service}}辦事處撤退<ref name=Hosken/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/05/SA-earthquake-claims-its-first-life |newspaper=EWN |date=2014-08-05 |accessdate=2014-08-05 |title=SA earthquake claims first life |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCtELvw?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/05/SA-earthquake-claims-its-first-life |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Rondganger |first1=Lee |title=Quake sets off ripple of fear |url=http://www.iol.co.za/dailynews/news/quake-sets-off-ripple-of-fear-1.1731192#.U-ynZOOSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=Daily News |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rox8IwMo?url=http://www.iol.co.za/dailynews/news/quake-sets-off-ripple-of-fear-1.1731192#.U-ynZOOSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。地球科學委員會地震組組長米歇爾·格羅貝拉表示，由於「沙灘的沙子容易令地面運動變強」，所以德班也能感到震動<ref>{{cite news |last1=Coan |first1=Stephen |title=Why Durban felt the quake |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Why-Durban-felt-the-quake-20140806 |newspaper=The Witness |accessdate=2014-08-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RvMF00AB?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Why-Durban-felt-the-quake-20140806 |archivedate=2014-08-18 |date=2014-08-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在莫桑比克[[馬普托|馬普托]]，身在大廈的人也要撤離<ref name=MG>{{cite news |title=SA earthquake big, but not uncommon |url=http://mg.co.za/article/2014-08-05-sa-earthquake-big-but-not-uncommon |accessdate=2014-08-15 |work=Mail & Guardian |agency=SAPA |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rqemttry?url=http://mg.co.za/article/2014-08-05-sa-earthquake-big-but-not-uncommon |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[津巴布韋|津巴布韋]]氣象局證實，津巴布韋未受此次地震影響<ref>{{cite news |last1=Chikwati |first1=Elita |title=Zimbabwe: SA Earthquake – Zim Safe |url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201408070262.html |newspaper=The Herald |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808054744/http://allafrica.com/stories/201408070262.html |archivedate=2014-08-08 |date=2014-08-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 傷亡 ===
地震唯一一名死者是一個名叫萊紹莫·馬卡奥拉（Leshomo Makhaola）的[[萊索托|萊索托]]人（31歲）；地震期間，他在西北省{{en-link|卡納納|Kanana, North West}}被一幅塌下來的舊礦房牆壁壓死<ref name=MN/><ref name=Brace>{{cite news |title=Brace for more quake shakes |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/brace-for-more-quake-shakes-1.1731411#.U-ykO-OSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-14 |newspaper=The Star |agency=SAPA |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RowKHvO0?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/brace-for-more-quake-shakes-1.1731411#.U-ykO-OSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Man-rescued-from-collapsed-house-after-quake-20140805 |title=Man rescued from collapsed house after quake |publisher=News24 |agency=SAPA |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCI24sr?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Man-rescued-from-collapsed-house-after-quake-20140805 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-08-23 }}</ref><ref name=sanews>{{cite news |title=Cabinet sends condolences to family of quake victim |url=http://sanews.gov.za/south-africa/cabinet-sends-condolences-family-quake-victim |newspaper=South African Government News Agency |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCQDcNq?url=http://sanews.gov.za/south-africa/cabinet-sends-condolences-family-quake-victim |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{en-link|ER24緊急醫療服務|ER24 Emergency Medical Services|ER24}}[[緊急醫療服務|緊急醫療服務]]的一名發言人表示，據報有礦工在奧克尼一個礦場被困，被困礦工分佈於11口礦井之內<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/local/2014/08/05/miners-trapped-after-5.3-earthquake-hits-south-africa |title=Miners trapped after 5.3 earthquake hits South Africa |date=2014-08-05 |accessdate=2014-08-05 |agency=South African Press Association |newspaper=News24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rozq2x1l?url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/local/2014/08/05/miners-trapped-after-5.3-earthquake-hits-south-africa |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>；但是隨後的檢查卻發現在當地工作的礦工安然無恙<ref name=Injured/><ref name=BBC1/>。截至8月5日19時30分（[[南非標準時間|南非標準時間]]），{{en-link|英美黃金阿散蒂|AngloGold Ashanti}}大莫利瓜（Great Noligwa）和摩押科聰（Moab Khotsong）礦場（位於奧克尼附近）全部3,300名身處地下的礦工（包括34名傷者）都已經救出地面 <ref name=Injured/><ref name=Cokayne>{{cite news |last1=Cokayne |first1=Roy |last2=Faku |first2=Dineo |title=Miners, markets survive earthquake |url=http://www.iol.co.za/business/companies/miners-markets-survive-earthquake-1.1731033#.U_GpRsWSyyg |accessdate=2014-08-18 |newspaper=Business Report |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rukiog1V?url=http://www.iol.co.za/business/companies/miners-markets-survive-earthquake-1.1731033#.U_GpRsWSyyg |archivedate=2014-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。全部34名傷者都只是受輕傷，他們身受裂傷、瘀傷，甚至腳骨骨折。他們到醫院接受治理<ref name=Hosken/><ref name=Cokayne/>，並在8月6日悉數出院<ref name=Sowetan>{{cite news |url=http://www.sowetanlive.co.za/news/2014/08/06/34-miners-discharged-from-hospital-after-earthquake |title=34 Miners discharged from hospital after earthquake |newspaper=The Sowetan |agency=SAPA |date=2014-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqD07xUc?url=http://www.sowetanlive.co.za/news/2014/08/06/34-miners-discharged-from-hospital-after-earthquake |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。礦場供電系統的運作一度中斷，而在供電系統大致恢復正常運作的時候，英美黃金阿散蒂的管理人員便開始進行疏散程序；礦場管理人員與在地下工作的礦工隊以電話聯絡，而礦井工程師則確定礦井設施能夠正常運作<ref name=Cokayne/><ref name=Protocol>{{cite news |url=http://www.bdlive.co.za/business/mining/2014/08/07/safety-protocols-worked-in-quake-evacuation-says-anglogold |title=Safety protocols worked in quake evacuation says Anglogold |newspaper=Business Day |date=2014-08-07 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RoxbWfJR?url=http://www.bdlive.co.za/business/mining/2014/08/07/safety-protocols-worked-in-quake-evacuation-says-anglogold |archivedate=2014-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。英美黃金阿散蒂的緊急醫護人員治理受傷礦工<ref name=Hosken/>，而輔導員則負責輔導感到震驚的員工<ref name=Protocol/>。隨後，大莫利瓜和摩押科聰礦場的採礦作業亦告停止，以進行安全檢查<ref name=Brace/><ref name=Sowetan/><ref name=Protocol/>。

=== 損壞 ===
地震令奧克尼和周邊地區的建築物受到嚴重破壞。位於史蒂爾方丹附近的庫瑪（Khuma）[[鎮區_(南非)|鎮區]]是重災區之一，當地超過600座房屋受地震破壞<ref name=Relief>{{cite news |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Relief-fund-opened-for-North-West-quake-victims-20140807 |title=Relief fund opened for North West quake victims |newspaper=News24 |agency=SAPA |date=2014-08-07 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDqi8VV?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Relief-fund-opened-for-North-West-quake-victims-20140807 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=Shevel>{{cite news |last1=Shevel |first1=Adele |title=Insurers brace for a wave of quake claims |url=http://www.bdlive.co.za/businesstimes/2014/08/10/insurers-brace-for-a-wave-of-quake-claims |accessdate=2014-08-15 |newspaper=Business Day |date=2014-08-10 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqNXjKIA?url=http://www.bdlive.co.za/businesstimes/2014/08/10/insurers-brace-for-a-wave-of-quake-claims |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。8月5日，當地又再發生餘震，當時庫瑪居民正在評估其居所的損毀情況<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news24.com/news24/SouthAfrica/News/Residents-scramble-as-aftershock-hits-20140805 |title=Residents scramble as aftershock hits |newspaper=News24 |date=2014-08-05 |accessdate=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqD8CxN0?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Residents-scramble-as-aftershock-hits-20140805 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Earthquake aftershock hits Orkney township |url=http://www.citypress.co.za/politics/earthquake-aftershock-hits-orkney-township/ |newspaper=City Press |accessdate=2014-08-06 |date=2014-08-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqCa2w0a?url=http://www.citypress.co.za/politics/earthquake-aftershock-hits-orkney-township/ |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。西北省共有3座診所受地震破壞，其中有2座診所需要關閉<ref name=Injured/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.enca.com/three-north-west-clinics-damaged-sa-quake |title=Three North West clinics damaged in SA quake |accessdate=2014-08-07 |newspaper=eNCA |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDCSzLx?url=http://www.enca.com/three-north-west-clinics-damaged-sa-quake |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。地震還破壞了2所學校；由於課室嚴重損毀，部分學生未能回校上課<ref>{{cite news |title=Pupils miss class due to quake damage |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Pupils-miss-class-due-to-quake-damage-20140806 |newspaper=News24 |agency=SAPA |accessdate=2014-08-06 |date=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDffl7U?url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Pupils-miss-class-due-to-quake-damage-20140806 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

地震發生後數天，南非大部分主要銀行和保險公司開始收到索償申請表。截至2014年8月6日，{{en-link|巴克萊非洲集團|Barclays Africa Group|南非聯合銀行}}（ABSA）收到200份索償申請表，[[標準銀行|標準銀行]]收到129份索償申請表，而{{en-link|耆衛集團|Old Mutual|Mutual & Federal}}保險公司則收到11份索償申請表<ref>{{cite news |last1=Molosankwe |first1=Botho |agency=SAPA |title=Claims pouring in after quake |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/claims-pouring-in-after-quake-1.1731742#.U-Och6iSySo |newspaper=IOL |accessdate=2014-08-07 |date=2014-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDJoCN7?url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/gauteng/claims-pouring-in-after-quake-1.1731742#.U-Och6iSySo |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 反應 ==
地球科學委員會警告，預計地震後數天仍會發生餘震，而這種現象可能會持續數個月。他們建議，如果發生餘震，所有身處於建築物的人都要疏散<ref name=Raaff/><ref name=Brace/>。

{{en-link|南非礦業部|Department of Mineral Resources (South Africa)|礦業部}}礦業檢察長大衛·姆西扎（David Msiza）要求克萊克斯多普、卡雷頓維爾、[[羅斯頓堡|羅斯頓堡]]等受災地區的礦業公司在地下進行檢查，以保證沒有礦工被困，並保證礦工的工作狀況安全<ref name=Cokayne/>。

英美黄金阿散蒂拒絕為地震負責，並表示地震發生地點位於該公司礦業設施以外<ref name=Crowley/>。

[[西北省省長|西北省省長]]蘇普拉·馬胡馬佩羅（Supra Mahumapelo）向該省居民承諾，所有受地震影響的災民會得到援助<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mosamo |first1=Sebabatso |title=Cause of SA earthquake uncertain |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/SA-earthquake-cause-uncertain |newspaper=EWN |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808071112/http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/SA-earthquake-cause-uncertain |archivedate=2014-08-08 |date=2014-08-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。馬胡馬佩羅表示，為災民提供的服務設施包括輔導和社會救濟服務，以及臨時住房<ref name=Relief/>。他說受地震破壞的建築物和基建設施需要用幾年的時間來修復<ref>{{cite news |title=Disaster relief fund to assist earthquake victims |url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/Disaster-Relief-Fund-established-for-earthquake-victims |newspaper=EWN |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RqDwB6HM?url=http://ewn.co.za/2014/08/06/Disaster-Relief-Fund-established-for-earthquake-victims |archivedate=2014-08-15 |date=2014-08-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[西北省_(南非)|西北省]]政府已設立西北省賑災基金，以協助該省受地震影響的居民<ref name=sanews/>。

西北省{{en-link|肯尼思·卡翁達博士地區|Dr Kenneth Kaunda District Municipality}}當局把調查隊派遣到該區各地，調查地震對該區造成的破壞<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sello|first1=Lenyaro|title=Fear grips Orkney community after earthquake|url=http://www.enca.com/fear-grips-orkney-community-after-earthquake|publisher=eNCA|accessdate=2014-08-16|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.enca.com%2Ffear-grips-orkney-community-after-earthquake&date=2014-08-16|archivedate=2014-08-16|date=2014-08-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

